MOVIE PLOT:- The Bamboo Saucer (1968)
An unidentified flying object is reported to have landed in a small Chinese village. Teams from the United States and Soviet Union race to get to it first.
A flying saucer hidden in a Red Chinese peasant village is sought by teams from the United States and U.S.S.R. On finding it, they band together to explore the saucer and take a trip into space.
"IT LANDED HERE...IN RED CHINA!" These words trigger the most incredible life-and-death struggle between RUSSIA and the UNITED STATES...who would be first to find this fantastic machine from outer space and unlock its awesome secrets!
